            "height": 424,
            "content": "## CRM New Lead → Instant SMS + AI Qualification Call\n\n**How it works:**\n1. Receives new lead from CRM via webhook\n2. Normalizes lead data across CRM platforms (HubSpot, Salesforce, Pipedrive)\n3. Creates/updates contact in Aloware with lead score + source\n4. Sends instant personalized SMS within seconds\n5. Routes by lead score: hot leads → AI Qualification call, warm leads → nurture sequence\n\n**Setup:**\n- Set n8n Variables: `ALOWARE_API_TOKEN`, `ALOWARE_LINE_PHONE`, `ALOWARE_HOT_SEQUENCE_ID`, `ALOWARE_NURTURE_SEQUENCE_ID`, `LEAD_SCORE_THRESHOLD`, `COMPANY_NAME`\n- Configure CRM to POST new leads to this webhook URL\n- Create 2 Aloware Sequences (hot AI qualification + warm nurture)"
